C is correct, or C is a solution, if ∀𝜏 ∈ Ω. 𝜏 |=𝑐𝑜𝑛𝑠 C𝑠 =⇒ 𝜏 |= I. In our example any C that
contains 𝑠𝑡𝑟𝑜𝑛𝑔(withdraw,withdraw) is correct for all traces that execute withdraw, as it would
