We extend Peepco with a new weaker type of consistency constraint, 𝑑𝑒𝑙𝑎𝑦, shown in Fig. 14.
The figure shows a logical interpretation of 𝑑𝑒𝑙𝑎𝑦 and the relationships of the involved actions that
